
        Requirements

# Users should be able to sign up
# Users should be able to login
# Users should be able to post
# Users should be able to comment a post
# System should push notiication
# System should be available 7/24


        API Design

/users
/users/{userId}
/users/{userId}/profile

/posts
/posts?user={userId}
/posts/{postId}

/comments
/comments?postId={postId}
/comments?userId={userId}
/comments?postId={postId}&userId={userId}
/comments/{commentId}

/likes
/likes?postId={postId}
/likes?user={userId}
/Likes?postId={postId}&userId={userId}
/likes/{likeId}

